<view class="content"><view class="self-info"><view class="input-column-top"><text class="input-huge-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>您想要报名的班级</text><radio-group class="class-group"><block wx:for="{{campClasses}}" wx:for-item="campClass" wx:for-index="__i0__" wx:key="id"><radio value="{{campClass.id}}" data-classes="{{campClass.id}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['classesChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">{{campClass.name}}</radio></block></radio-group></view><text class="input-huge-title">一、基本信息</text><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>1.申请人姓名</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','name','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{name}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>2.性别</text><radio-group class="gender-group"><radio value="m" data-gender="m" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['genderChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">男</radio><radio value="f" data-gender="f" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['genderChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">女</radio></radio-group></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>3.出生日期</text><picker mode="date" value="{{birthday}}" start="1900-01-01" end="{{endDate}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['birthdayChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="input-column-box">{{birthday}}</view></picker></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>4.联系电话</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','telephone','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{telephone}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>5.常用微信</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','wechat','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{wechat}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>6.常用邮箱</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['blur',[['checkEmail']]],['input',[['__set_model',['','email','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{email}}" bindblur="__e" bindinput="__e"/><view hidden="{{!(showAlert)}}" class="alertion">邮箱不合法</view></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>7.常驻城市</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','city','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{city}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><text class="input-huge-title">二、教育/工作背景</text><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>1.最高学历</text><radio-group class="class-group"><radio value="PhD" data-education="PhD" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">博士研究生</radio><radio value="MBA" data-education="MBA" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">硕士研究生</radio><radio value="Bachelor" data-education="Bachelor" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">本科</radio><radio value="College" data-education="College" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">专科</radio><radio value="Others" data-education="Others" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">其他</radio></radio-group></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>2.最高学历毕业毕业院校及起止时间</text><text class="explanation">如：2004-2008/北京大学/计算机科学/学士</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','educationTime','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{educationTime}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>3.您创业前所在公司、职位及时间（包括国王创业经历）</text><text class="explanation">如：2010-2015/好未来/产品经理</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','experience','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{experience}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><text class="input-huge-title">三、公司/项目信息</text><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>1.公司品牌名称</text><text class="explanation">公司主营业务/产品名称，请确保据此能够搜索到您的网站/公众号/App；<view class="_br"></view>如尚未发布，填写“无”</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','brand','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{brand}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>2.公司网址</text><text class="explanation">如尚未发布，填写“无”</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','website','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{website}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>3.App或公众号名称</text><text class="explanation">如尚未发布，填写“无”</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','application','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{application}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>4.公司成立时间</text><picker mode="date" value="{{date}}" start="1900-01-01" end="{{endDate}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['bindDateChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="input-column-box">{{date}}</view></picker></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>5.公司总部所在城市</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','companyCity','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{companyCity}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>6.公司员工数量（单位：人）</text><input class="input-column-box" type="number" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','membership','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{membership}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>7.您在企业中的职位</text><radio-group class="class-group"><radio value="F" data-education="F" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">创始人</radio><radio value="CF" data-education="CF" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">联合创始人</radio><radio value="P" data-education="P" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">董事长</radio><radio value="CEO" data-education="CEO" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">CEO</radio><radio value="Others" data-education="Others" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['educationChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">其他</radio></radio-group></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>8.公司项目介绍</text><text class="explanation">为使面试组更好的了解您的公司/项目，烦请您认真填写</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','abstract','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{abstract}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>9.公司主要运营数据</text><text class="explanation">如：对于在线类业务，如注册用户量、应用下载量、日活/周活/月活等；对于线下业务，如学员数/用户数、市场覆盖率等</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','output','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{output}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>10.上一年公司收入规模（单位：万元）</text><text class="explanation">最近一年的收入</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','income','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{income}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column-top"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>11.公司目前融资情况</text><radio-group class="class-group"><radio value="N" data-finance="N" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">尚未获得投资</radio><radio value="seed/angel" data-finance="seed/angel" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">已完成种子/天使融资</radio><radio value="pre-A" data-finance="pre-A" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">已完成pre-A轮融资</radio><radio value="A" data-finance="A" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">已完成A轮融资</radio><radio value="refuse" data-finance="refuse" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">不方便透露</radio><radio value="others" data-finance="others" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">其他</radio></radio-group></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>12.公司目前估值（单位：万元）</text><text class="explanation">如果暂无估值或不方便透露，可填写“0”</text><input class="input-column-box" type="number" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','price','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{price}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title">13.关于您的公司/项目还有哪些补充说明，请在此填写</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','addition','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{addition}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><text class="input-huge-title">四、关于推荐人</text><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>推荐人信息1:（姓名／公司／职位）</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','referee1','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{referee1}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title">推荐人信息2:（姓名／公司／职位）</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','referee2','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{referee2}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title">推荐人信息3:（姓名／公司／职位）</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','referee3','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{referee3}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><text class="input-huge-title">五、其他信息</text><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>1.未来之星创新院名额宝贵，培训统一安排时间内，不接受因个人活动冲突的请假理由，如缺勤达到总课程的1/3将被劝退，您是否接受此考勤要求？（是/否）</text><input class="input-column-box" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','ifagree','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{ifagree}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>2.请简述您的申请理由（100字以内）</text><textarea class="long-text" length="100" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','reason','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{reason}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title">3.您能为创新院的其他学员做出哪些贡献？</text><textarea data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','contribution','$event',[]]]]]]}}" class="long-text" value="{{contribution}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="input-column"><text class="input-column-title"><text class="highlight">*</text>4.您通过何种渠道了解到“未来创新院”？</text><radio-group class="class-group"><radio value="weixin" data-finance="weixin" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">微信朋友圈</radio><radio value="friend" data-finance="friend" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">朋友推荐</radio><radio value="Pubaccount" data-finance="Pubaccount" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">未来之星公众号：EdStars未来同学会</radio><radio value="web" data-finance="web" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">好未来官网</radio><radio value="media" data-finance="media" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">媒体报道</radio><radio value="others" data-finance="others" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['financeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">其他</radio></radio-group></view><view class="input-column"><text class="promise">未来之星创新院组委会承诺：以上所有信息仅供组委会了解申请人及项目情况，组委会承诺不会向任何第三方透露；祝您一切顺利！</text><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['saveMessage',['$event']]]]]}}" class="save-btn" bindtap="__e">确认报名</button></view></view></view>